d before preservation of any new artifacts.\\n\\nPaths to inspect: `logs/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/failure-analysis/codex_failure_analysis_issue_2123.log` (no preserved CI run log was found for the failing job), `local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-60aefe3e/script_run_metrics/add_new_library_support.json`, `local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-60aefe3e/script_run_metrics/fix_javac_fail.json`, and the existing baseline test at `tests/src/io.undertow/undertow-parser-generator/2.2.19.Final/src/test/java/io_undertow/undertow_parser_generator/Undertow_parser_generatorTest.java`.\\n\\n1. Re-run the `javaTest`/compatibility lane for `io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1` with full Gradle `--stacktrace` and retain the raw task logs.\\n2. Compare the existing `2.2.19.Final` baseline test and dependency graph against `2.4.0.RC1` to identify any API or runtime behavior change that breaks the Java run.\\n3. If the RC1 run is reproducibly failing, either adapt the test for the new version or record `2.4.0.RC1` as unsupported until a passing run is available.\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-04-27T16:16:53Z\",\"includesCreatedEdit\":false,\"isMinimized\":false,\"minimizedReason\":\"\",\"reactionGroups\":[],\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2123#issuecomment-4328606598\",\"viewerDidAuthor\":true},{\"id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABAimpcg\",\"author\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\"},\"authorAssociation\":\"MEMBER\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job for `io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1` failed (`fails-java-run`, workflow status `failure`, reason `job_failed`).\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2123-fails-java-run-io.undertow-undertow-parser-generator-2.4.0.RC1-0bc9b2cb\\n\\nMost likely failing stage: the Java runtime test phase (`:test` under `:tckTest`). In `human-intervention-logs/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-27T23-33-20-350454Z.log`, all 6 `Undertow_parser_generatorTest` cases fail in `io.undertow.annotationprocessor.AbstractParserGenerator.createTokenizer(...)` because `org.jboss.classfilewriter.DefaultClassFactory` cannot initialize: `java.lang.IllegalAccessException: module java.base does not open java.lang to unnamed module`, followed by `ExceptionInInitializerError` and `NoClassDefFoundError`. The run metrics show no automated fix was produced: `local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/.pending_metrics.json` and `local_repositories/forge_run_metrics/2123-3b33bb3d/script_run_metrics/fix_java_run_fail.json` record `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, identical starting/ending commits, `generated_loc: 0`, `metadata_entries: 0`, and `code_coverage_percent: 0.0` (dynamic-access coverage unavailable).\\n\\nLogs worth inspecting:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-27T23-33-20-350454Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/failure-analysis/codex_failure_analysis_issue_2123.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`\\n- `build/tests/io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1/*.out`\\n\\n1. Reproduce with `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.undertow:undertow-parser-generator:2.4.0.RC1 --stacktrace` and verify whether the test JVM needs `--add-opens=java.base/java.lang=ALL-UNNAMED`.\\n2. Compare the `2.4.0.RC1` runtime setup against the working `2.2.19.Final` baseline, especially the `jboss-classfilewriter` dependency and any version-specific test JVM args.\\n3. If this module-access failure is expected for the current JDK/version combination, update the version-specific test setup accordingly or mark `2.4.0.RC1` unsupported and rerun the Java and native lanes.\",\"creat