https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-04T01:24:15Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-04T01:24:15Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nForge rechecked this PR for the new-library coverage publication blocker on 2026-05-04. The branch head `58c4d49f8b65595d7abe8629adf31cf769b174b9` still has review-blocking dynamic-access coverage: `stats/org.jboss.modules/jboss-modules/2.1.6.Final/stats.json` reports `0/57` covered calls (`0%`, with `46` reflection and `11` resource calls), and `metadata/org.jboss.modules/jboss-modules/2.1.6.Final/reachability-metadata.json` is still empty. New-library PRs with dynamic-access calls need at least `50%` coverage before `human-intervention` can be removed.\\n\\nValidation rerun against this branch in an isolated worktree:\\n\\n- Passed: `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.jboss.modules:jboss-modules:2.1.6.Final --stacktrace`\\n- Passed: `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.jboss.modules:jboss-modules:2.1.6.Final --stacktrace`\\n- Passed: `./gradlew generateDynamicAccessCoverageReport generateLibraryStats -Pcoordinates=org.jboss.modules:jboss-modules:2.1.6.Final --stacktrace`\\n\\nThe Gradle rerun did not make the PR reviewable: regenerated dynamic-access evidence still reports `0/57` coverage. No branch push or label cleanup is appropriate from this pass.\\n\\nNext owner: strengthen the JBoss Modules tests until the dynamic-access report reaches at least `29/57` covered calls, refresh generated metadata and stats, push the PR branch, then request re-review. Keep `human-intervention` until that evidence is present.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4367694320/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null}]\n/tmp/rhei-issue-timeline/5203.json:1:[{\"id\":25107733036,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABBJaNec8AAAAF2ImaLA\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25107733036\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"graalvmbot\",\"id\":17270325,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MjcwMzI1\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/17270325?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/graalvmbot\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/graalvmbot/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"labeled\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T1