jovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T15:57:40Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T15:57:40Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `io.netty:netty-codec-smtp:4.2.2.Final`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-5203-fails-native-image-run-io.netty-netty-codec-smtp-4.2.2.Final-1e47f610\\n\\nThe failure appears to be in the metadata-generation/bootstrap stage of `:fixTestNativeImageRun`, before a new `4.2.2.Final` native-image run actually started. The top-level Gradle daemon log at `/home/vjovanov/.gradle/daemon/9.1.0/daemon-3742815.out.log` shows `Execution failed for task ':fixTestNativeImageRun'` while `Generating metadata...`. The nested test-project daemon log at `/home/vjovanov/.gradle/daemon/9.1.0/daemon-3744276.out.log` shows the concrete cause: `[native-image-plugin] Instrumenting task with the native-image-agent: test`, then `Could not find agent library native-image-agent on the library path, with error: libnative-image-agent.so: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory`, followed by `Process 'Gradle Test Executor 1' finished with non-zero exit value 1`. The local test result `/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5203-5ca02869/tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.1.74.Final/build/test-results/test/TEST-Gradle#20Test#20Run#20#3atest.xml` records the same executor crash with no stdout/stderr. No workflow run logs were preserved locally, and no `4.2.2.Final` metrics were produced; `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final` was never generated, `metadata/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final/` is empty, and there is no `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final/execution-metrics.json`.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `/home/vjovanov/.gradle/daemon/9.1.0/daemon-3742815.out.log`\\n- `/home/vjovanov/.gradle/daemon/9.1.0/daemon-3744276.out.log`\\n- `/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5203-5ca02869/tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.1.74.Final/build/test-results/test/TEST-Gradle#20Test#20Run#20#3atest.xml`\\n- `/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5203-5ca02869/build/reports/problems/problems-report.html`\\n- `/home/vjovanov/c/forge/forge1/graalvm-reachability-metadata/forge/local_repositories/forge_worktrees/5203-5ca02869/tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.1.74.Final/build/reports/problems/problems-report.html`\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n1. Re-run the `fixTestNativeImageRun` flow in an environment where the GraalVM `native-image-agent` shared library is installed and visible on the test JVM library path.\\n2. Confirm that the rerun actually creates `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final` and `metadata/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final/reachability-metadata.json` before investigating any library-specific native-image regression.\\n3. If it still fails after the agent-library issue is fixed, capture the new workflow/native-image logs and the `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-smtp/4.2.2.Final` outputs for follow-up.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4366570182/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"foll