ttps://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T03:56:19Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-28T03:56:19Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `fails-java-run` job failed for `xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01` with workflow status `failure`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2574-fails-java-run-xml-apis-xml-apis-1.2.01-8fda82cb\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the initial Java runtime test reproduction/fix stage (`test`/`javaTest`). Concrete evidence: no matching run logs were preserved, run metrics and dynamic-access coverage are unavailable, the preserved branch was created from `HEAD` and pushed with no additional commit, and there is no generated `tests/src/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/`, `metadata/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/`, or `stats/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/` tree in the preserved worktree. This suggests the job failed before it produced any recoverable `1.2.01` artifacts.\\n\\nPaths to inspect:\\n- `forge_run_metrics/2574-1506b5af/logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/` (expected workflow logs; not present in the scratch metrics repo)\\n- `human-intervention-logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/` (expected copied logs on the preserved branch; not present)\\n- `tests/src/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/build/test-results/test/` and `tests/src/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/build/reports/tests/test/` after reproducing locally\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01 --stacktrace` to capture the first runtime failure.\\n2. If the `1.2.01` test scaffold is still missing, compare against `tests/src/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.0.b2/` and decide whether a concrete runtime test needs to be added or adapted before retrying.\\n3. Preserve the Gradle output under `human-intervention-logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/` or attach it to this issue, then continue the version-bump fix manually.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4332247144/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":24931962688,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAq4s3M8AAAAFzg-PQA\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/24931962688\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\