ers/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:39:44Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4364289900\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2574#issuecomment-4364289900\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2574\",\"id\":4364289900,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBCHHbA\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:53:30Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:53:30Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `fails-java-run` job failed for `xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2574-fails-java-run-xml-apis-xml-apis-1.2.01-4a91c442\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the `fix-java-run-fail` generation/orchestration step after the original JVM failure was reproduced. The raw Gradle log at `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-42-48-440922Z.log` shows the real failure: `Xml_apisTest > versionClassReportsXmlCommonsIdentity()` failed because actual `\\\"1.2.01\\\"` did not contain expected `\\\"1.0\\\"` at `Xml_apisTest.java:74`. After that, `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T16-43-43-207622Z.log` shows the automation struggling with source-context resolution (`find: ‘local_repositories/source_context/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/main’: No such file or directory`), and `stats/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/execution-metrics.json` shows `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, `metadata_file: None`, with the same starting and ending commit (`af4b76c33bf1b9d99f5100e78e9751f3911cbe0b`).\\n\\nLater retries do not show a persistent library/runtime failure: `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-43-43-219421Z.log` and `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-49-43-666186Z.log` both report `versionClassReportsXmlCommonsIdentity()` and all 10 tests passing. There is also a separate metadata detour in `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/metadata-fix/codex.log`, which does not match the original assertion-based `fails-java-run` problem. Dynamic-access coverage is unavailable for this run.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-42-48-440922Z.log`\\n- `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T16-43-43-207622Z.log`\\n- `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-43-43-219421Z.log`\\n- `logs/xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01/metadata-fix/codex.log`\\n- `stats/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/execution-metrics.json`\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n1. Recreate the original JVM failure and verify whether `versionClassReportsXmlCommonsIdentity()` should assert `1.2.01` (or a broader `1.2`-series value) instead of `1.0`.\\n2. Ignore the metadata-fix detour unless a clean rerun proves `metadata/xml-apis/xml-apis/1.2.01/reachability-metadata.json` is actually required.\\n3. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=xml-apis:xml-apis:1.2.01` from a clean worktree, then regenerate stats if needed so the final fix and coverage are captured cleanly.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4364289900/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},