tps://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T16:14:51Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4360490930\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/3645#issuecomment-4360490930\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/3645\",\"id\":4360490930,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABA-fPsg\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T16:53:15Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-01T16:53:15Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6`. Preserved work is available on https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-3645-library-new-request-net.sf.saxon-Saxon-HE-9.9.1-6-d98823e5.\\n\\nAlthough the run was classified as `test_generation_failed`, the preserved work suggests generation mostly succeeded and the likely blocker is the native test validation stage. The generation branch reached commit `4291afc9735787fcc5ced03dd697337235c99efe` with dynamic-access coverage `34/34`, but `build/tests/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/c35116e37832c3899b684b6cc8082941.out` shows `:nativeTest FAILED` with 11 failing tests, including `BuiltInFunctionSetTest`, `ConfigurationTest`, `DynamicLoaderTest`, `PJConverter*`, and `StyleNodeFactoryTest`. The repeated root cause is reflective instantiation of classes that do not have a public zero-arg constructor, especially `net.sf.saxon.Configuration` and `net.sf.saxon.functions.UpperCase` (`InstantiationException` / `NoSuchMethodException`). The metrics file `stats/net.sf.saxon/Saxon-HE/9.9.1-6/execution-metrics.json` also ends in `failure` after 12 iterations and records no accepted artifact (`generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, `metadata_file: None`), so the automation never reconciled the generated work with a passing validation run.\\n\\nPlease inspect `human-intervention-logs/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T16-40-46-728013Z.log`, `human-intervention-logs/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T16-48-21-648164Z.log`, `build/tests/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/c35116e37832c3899b684b6cc8082941.out`, and `stats/net.sf.saxon/Saxon-HE/9.9.1-6/execution-metrics.json`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Check out the preserved branch and review the generated tests under `tests/src/net.sf.saxon/Saxon-HE/9.9.1-6`.\\n2. Rework or drop tests that assume reflective `Class#newInstance()` succeeds for `Configuration` or built-in function classes without public zero-arg constructors, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6`.\\n3. If validation passes, use the preserved branch as the starting point for the manual PR.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4360490930/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{