",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T11:11:27Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4366046250\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/3645#issuecomment-4366046250\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/3645\",\"id\":4366046250,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDyUKg\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T11:23:50Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T11:23:50Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job for `net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6` failed. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-3645-library-new-request-net.sf.saxon-Saxon-HE-9.9.1-6-ad73d28a\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the add-new-library-support/test-generation handoff, not Gradle or Native Image execution. The generation log says it added `ConfigurationTest.java` and updated metadata, and the Gradle/native logs then show 9 passing tests, including 8 `ConfigurationTest` cases. However, the preserved worktree still only contains the scaffold `Saxon_HETest.java`, while `stats/net.sf.saxon/Saxon-HE/9.9.1-6/execution-metrics.json` reports `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, and `metadata_file: None`. Separately, the generated dynamic-access report still ends at `14/34` covered calls (`41.18%`), so coverage remains below the 50% minimum for a `library-new-request`.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `logs/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-03T11-20-29-109821Z.log`\\n- `logs/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T11-20-29-145897Z.log`\\n- `logs/net.sf.saxon:Saxon-HE:9.9.1-6/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T11-21-38-689442Z.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Recover or recreate the missing `ConfigurationTest.java` in the preserved branch so the source matches the passing compiled/test artifacts.\\n2. Extend coverage beyond `net.sf.saxon.Configuration` to the remaining uncovered dynamic-access classes reported in the dynamic-access report, especially `net.sf.saxon.pull.StaxBridge` and `net.sf.saxon.trans.DynamicLoader`, until total coverage is above 50%.\\n3. Re-run the library test lane and confirm the preserved branch actually contains the generated source files and recorded artifact paths before re-triggering automation.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/com