\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBBmFhg\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-02T12:09:51Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-02T12:09:51Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `fails-java-run` job failed for `com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4254-fails-java-run-com.android.tools.build-builder-model-2.1.2-7c864b9d\\n\\nThe primary library-specific failure appears to be the JVM test stage: `Builder_modelTest.exposesStableVersionArtifactOutputAndSeverityConstants()` still expects `\\\"2.1.0\\\"` but the runtime value is `\\\"2.1.2\\\"`, so `:test` fails immediately. See `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T10-28-59-874133Z.log`.\\n\\nThe preserved verification loop then got stuck in native trace verification rather than producing a fix. `runNativeTraceImage` repeatedly fails with `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter`, including in `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-92-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-02T12-01-55-871938Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-99-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-02T12-07-25-945663Z.log`. The run metrics also show no repo change was made: `stats/com.android.tools.build/builder-model/2.1.2/execution-metrics.json` reports `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, `generated_loc: 0`, `test_file: None`, and `metadata_file: None`.\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n1. Update the `2.1.2` test to stop asserting the old hard-coded `2.1.0` version value in `exposesStableVersionArtifactOutputAndSeverityConstants()`.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2` and then `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\\n3. If native verification still fails on `PostDiscoveryFilter`, investigate the JUnit platform resource registration issue separately from the `builder-model` test change before retrying automation.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4363748742/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",