0?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"id\":25095871781,\"node_id\":\"PVTISC_lADOHlghYc8AAAABBGNf5s8AAAAF19SdJQ\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25095871781\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:15:26Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4364228729\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4254#issuecomment-4364228729\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4254\",\"id\":4364228729,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBCDYeQ\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:20:39Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-02T16:20:39Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4254-fails-java-run-com.android.tools.build-builder-model-2.1.2-958fb82c\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the initial Java runtime test lane. In `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-02T16-17-06-254247Z.log`, `Builder_modelTest.exposesStableVersionArtifactOutputAndSeverityConstants()` fails because the test still expects `Version.ANDROID_GRADLE_PLUGIN_VERSION` to be `\\\"2.1.0\\\"` while `builder-model:2.1.2` returns `\\\"2.1.2\\\"`. The agent later identified exactly that one-line fix and logged a successful `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2 --stacktrace` in `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-02T16-18-14-228591Z.log`, but `stats/com.android.tools.build/builder-model/2.1.2/execution-metrics.json` still reports `status: failure`, `generated_loc: 0`, and no preserved test/metadata artifact. If you continue into native verification, also inspect `human-intervention-logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-02T16-18-39-783571Z.log`, which shows a `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter`.\\n\\n1. Restore the `tests/src/com.android.tools.build/builder-model/2.1.2/` test project from starting commit `dab97ba70a616f3f6919ae5a05e7b6fcca753939` and update `Builder_modelTest` to expect `\\\"2.1.2\\\"` instead of `\\\"2.1.0\\\"`.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2 --stacktrace` and then `./gradlew nativeTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\\n3. If native trace coverage is required, decide whether to add resource metadata for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter` based on the `runNativeTraceImage` log.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4364228729/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25095930227,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABBGNf5s8AAAAF19WBcw\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25095930227\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/star