/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:15:15Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365936969\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4254#issuecomment-4365936969\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4254\",\"id\":4365936969,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDrpSQ\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:19:47Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:19:47Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `fails-java-run` job failed for `com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4254-fails-java-run-com.android.tools.build-builder-model-2.1.2-2a4df406\\n\\nThe most likely library-specific failing stage is the JVM test run. In `logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T10-16-56-939952Z.log` and `logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/fix-java-run-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-03T10-17-34-208434Z.log`, `Builder_modelTest > exposesStableVersionArtifactOutputAndSeverityConstants()` fails because the test still expects `\\\"2.1.0\\\"` but the runtime value is `\\\"2.1.2\\\"`. Gradle then reports `Execution failed for task ':test'` and `Test for com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2 failed with exit code 1`. The metrics show the automation never produced a candidate fix: `stats/com.android.tools.build/builder-model/2.1.2/execution-metrics.json` reports `status: failure`, `iterations: 1`, `generated_loc: 0`, and no generated test or metadata artifacts.\\n\\nThere is also follow-up native verification noise worth checking after the Java test is fixed. `logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T10-02-38-256815Z.log` shows `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter`, and `logs/com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T10-17-59-271380Z.log` shows the same class of failure for `META-INF/services/javax.xml.stream.XMLOutputFactory` during JUnit XML reporting.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Update the `builder-model` test for `2.1.2` so it asserts the correct version value instead of the old hard-coded `2.1.0`.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2` and then `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=com.android.tools.build:builder-model:2.1.2`.\\n3. If native verification still fails after the test fix, inspect the two `native-test-verify` logs above and address the missing resource registrations separately from the library test change.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365936969/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25105545960,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABBGNf5s8AAAAF2Gg66A\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25105545960\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url