":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2889\",\"id\":4361304532,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABA_Q51A\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T19:51:23Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-01T19:51:23Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating`. Preserved work is available on the branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2889-library-new-request-org.apache.htrace-htrace-core-3.1.0-incubating-ff652950\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage is test generation/content review, not a current Gradle or native-image build break. The generation log shows the workflow explicitly chasing dynamic-access coverage for internal shaded classes such as `org.apache.htrace.fasterxml.jackson.databind.util.ArrayBuilders` (`human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T18-04-36-225948Z.log`). The generated tests are correspondingly dominated by shaded Jackson and commons-logging internals: for example, `BeanDeserializerBaseTest.java` imports `org.apache.htrace.fasterxml.jackson.databind.ObjectMapper`, and `LogFactoryImplTest.java` targets `org.apache.htrace.commons.logging.impl.LogFactoryImpl`. The final dynamic-access report is 100/103 covered, but the covered calls break down to 62 shaded Jackson, 32 commons-logging, and only 9 other HTrace calls (`tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`). A later replay in `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/metadata-fix/codex.log` shows `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating` succeeding with 52 native tests, 0 failures, and 1 aborted native test, which points to a quality/scope problem in the generated tests rather than an active infra failure. The run metrics also ended in failure after 43 iterations and 1753 generated LOC (`stats/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/execution-metrics.json`).\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T18-04-36-225948Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/metadata-fix/codex.log`\\n- `tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\\n- `tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Replace the shaded-Jackson/commons-logging-heavy generated tests with HTrace-specific tests that exercise public tracing behavior for this coordinate.\\n2. Review the preserved native tests for policy issues; `LogFactoryImplTest` currently aborts one native case instead of proving the behavior under native image.\\n3. Re-run `./gradlew checkMetadataFiles -Pcoordinates=org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating` and `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating` after narrowing the test set.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4361304532/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25081055837,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAuzEZs8AAAAF1vKKXQ\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25081055837\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com