aalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25105297615\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T09:49:29Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365904381\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2889#issuecomment-4365904381\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2889\",\"id\":4365904381,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDpp_Q\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:00:18Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T10:00:18Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `library-new-request` job failed for `org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating`. Preserved work is available on https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2889-library-new-request-org.apache.htrace-htrace-core-3.1.0-incubating-30b2bae9.\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was `add-new-library-support` / test-generation handoff rather than plain Gradle compilation. `stats/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/execution-metrics.json` shows `status: failure`, `generated_loc: 0`, `metadata_entries: 0`, `artifacts.test_file: None`, `artifacts.metadata_file: None`, and the starting/ending commit both stayed at `8135843f8f3d74b849252a51e1c86c7834c27b5c`. In the preserved worktree, the only test source still present is the scaffold `tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/src/test/java/org_apache_htrace/htrace_core/Htrace_coreTest.java`, and `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T09-56-59-676732Z.log` shows it printing “This is just a placeholder, implement your test”.\\n\\nThere is also a mismatch worth checking: `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-03T09-56-59-650333Z.log` ends with the agent claiming it added a focused `LogFactoryImplTest`, but those changes were not persisted in the preserved worktree and the metrics still report zero generated LOC. Dynamic-access coverage remained far below the new-library threshold: `tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json` reports `12/103` covered calls (`11.65%`). In addition, `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T09-58-11-389693Z.log` shows a `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter` during `runNativeTraceImage`, which may also be interfering with metadata tracing.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-03T09-56-59-650333Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T09-56-59-676732Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T09-58-11-389693Z.log`\\n- `tests/src/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\\n- `stats/org.apache.htrace/htrace-core/3.1.0-incubating/execution-metrics.json`\\n\\n1. Replace the scaffold test with a real library-specific test that exercises `org.apache.htrace.commons.logging.impl.LogFactoryImpl` and persist it on the preserved branch.\\n2. Re-run dynamic-access/native tracing for `org.apache.htrace:htrace-core:3.1.0-incubating` and verify coverage improves from `12/103` to at least the 50% new-library threshold.\\n3. Investigate and fix the `runNativeTraceImage` `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter` if it still reproduces.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365904381/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25105380376,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAuzEZs8AAAAF2GW0GA\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25105380376\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/ot