er\":{\"login\":\"kimeta\",\"id\":96449436,\"node_id\":\"U_kgDOBb-znA\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/96449436?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kimeta\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-01T13:49:43Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-01T13:49:43Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26`. Preserved work is available here:\\nhttps://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fkimeta%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4020-library-new-request-ch.qos.logback-logback-core-1.5.26-d420822e\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage is native-image test validation, not dynamic-access coverage generation. The run reached `41/41` dynamic-access coverage (100%), and the preserved branch includes the final coverage commit (`9726e2a2`, `Dynamic-access coverage for ch.qos.logback.core.util.FileUtil (41/41)`), but the Gradle output shows `> Task :nativeTest FAILED`. The clearest blocker is a native runtime `MissingReflectionRegistrationError` for `java.lang.String.serialVersionUID`, raised during serialization in `AutoFlushingObjectWriterTest` and again from the `RemoteReceiverStreamClient` path. The native test report also shows additional failing/generated tests in `AggregationAssessorTest`, `ConsoleAppenderTest`, `EnvUtilTest`, `PropertyEvalScriptBuilderTest`, and `StringToObjectConverterTest`, so the test suite is still not valid under native image.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T13-44-12-153305Z.log`\\n- `build/tests/ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26/86c8cc3152d43c49c818b5eaeeebef91.out`\\n- `tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/build/test-results/test-native/TEST-junit-jupiter.xml`\\n- `tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Fix the native-test blocker on the preserved branch, starting with the missing serialization/reflection metadata for `java.lang.String.serialVersionUID` or by rewriting the affected serialization tests to avoid that unsupported path.\\n2. Rework the brittle generated tests that still fail under native image (`AggregationAssessorTest`, `ConsoleAppenderTest`, `EnvUtilTest`, `PropertyEvalScriptBuilderTest`, `StringToObjectConverterTest`, `RemoteReceiverStreamClientTest`).\\n3. Rerun validation for `ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26` and update the issue once `:nativeTest` passes.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4359590021/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"kimeta\",\"id\":96449436,\"node_id\":\"U_kgDOBb-znA\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/96449436?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/kimeta\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/kimeta/followers\",\"following_ur