anov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T09:31:06Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365876974\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4020#issuecomment-4365876974\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4020\",\"id\":4365876974,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDn-7g\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T09:43:02Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T09:43:02Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4020-library-new-request-ch.qos.logback-logback-core-1.5.26-ab3c86fa\\n\\nMost likely failing stage: test generation/persistence. `stats/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/execution-metrics.json` shows `status: failure` after 1 iteration with `generated_loc: 0`, `metadata_entries: 0`, and both `artifacts.test_file` and `artifacts.metadata_file` set to `None`. The preserved branch still contains only the scaffold test at `tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/src/test/java/ch_qos_logback/logback_core/Logback_coreTest.java` and empty metadata at `metadata/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/reachability-metadata.json`, while `human-intervention-logs/ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-03T09-39-26-571737Z.log` shows an uncommitted attempt to replace that scaffold with a `ConsoleAppenderTest`.\\n\\nCoverage is still below the new-library threshold: `tests/src/ch.qos.logback/logback-core/1.5.26/build/reports/dynamic-access/dynamic-access-coverage.json` reports only 7/37 covered calls (18.92%), all on `ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender`. If you continue from that direction, also inspect `human-intervention-logs/ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T09-39-26-591708Z.log` for the two failing native `ConsoleAppenderTest` assertions and `human-intervention-logs/ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T09-40-54-233478Z.log` for the `MissingResourceRegistrationError` on `META-INF/services/org.junit.platform.launcher.PostDiscoveryFilter`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Replace the scaffold placeholder with real `logback-core` tests and commit both the tests and any required metadata to the preserved branch.\\n2. Either fix the attempted `ConsoleAppender`/Jansi path or broaden coverage so dynamic-access coverage clears the 50% gate for new-library support.\\n3. Resolve the native/resource-registration failure from `runNativeTraceImage`, then rerun `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=ch.qos.logback:logback-core:1.5.26`.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4365876974/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_e