/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T02:21:53Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4331957211\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565#issuecomment-4331957211\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565\",\"id\":4331957211,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABAjRr2w\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T02:34:13Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-28T02:34:13Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2565-fails-javac-compile-io.opentelemetry-opentelemetry-exporter-common-1.28.0-ccdd6277\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was `:compileTestJava` in the generated `tests/src/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0` project. The main evidence is in `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T02-26-28-452149Z.log`, where `RetryUtilTest.java` fails because it still imports `io.opentelemetry.exporter.internal.retry.RetryPolicy` and calls `RetryUtil.setRetryPolicyOnDelegate(...)`; those symbols existed in `1.19.0`, but they are no longer present in `1.28.0`. In `1.28.0`, `RetryUtil` only exposes the retryable code accessors, and `RetryPolicy` usage has moved under `io.opentelemetry.sdk.common.export`.\\n\\nA later automation pass appears to have pivoted to dynamic-access coverage work for `Authenticator` instead of landing the javac fix; see `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T02-29-46-144884Z.log`. This matches the run metrics summary (`Generated LOC: 0`, starting commit = ending commit `3d868106452baab2513581ef03ef9bbddb087da7`), so no corrective patch was actually preserved. The preserved branch currently contains the logs, but not a committed fix for the `1.28.0` test project.\\n\\nLogs and outputs worth inspecting:\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T02-26-28-452149Z.log`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T02-29-46-144884Z.log`\\n- `build/tests/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/a0a14a1545cfbcd9d7e1fc5b9da066ac.out`\\n- `build/tests/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/5b46da43df84f1c60307a96aed68fc3e.out`\\n- `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Recreate or restore `tests/src/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0` and update `RetryUtilTest` for the `1.28.0` API surface by removing the stale internal `RetryPolicy` / `setRetryPolicyOnDelegate(...)` coverage.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew compileTestJava -Pcoordinates=io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0` and then `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`.\\n3. If dynamic-access coverage is still expected after the javac fix, recover or re-add the `Authenticator` test path and rerun the coverage/reporting steps.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4331957211/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos