s{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"id\":24948597117,\"node_id\":\"PVTISC_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAq4nL88AAAAFzw1hfQ\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/24948597117\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"event\":\"project_v2_item_status_changed\",\"commit_id\":null,\"commit_url\":null,\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T13:04:13Z\",\"performed_via_github_app\":null},{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4335570936\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565#issuecomment-4335570936\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565\",\"id\":4335570936,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABAmuP-A\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-04-28T13:15:13Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-28T13:15:13Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2565-fails-javac-compile-io.opentelemetry-opentelemetry-exporter-common-1.28.0-a2ca9daf\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was `:compileTestJava`. In `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T13-09-08-376366Z.log`, `tests/src/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0/src/test/java/io_opentelemetry/opentelemetry_exporter_common/RetryUtilTest.java` still imports `io.opentelemetry.exporter.internal.retry.RetryPolicy` and calls `RetryPolicy.getDefault()`, but that symbol is missing in `1.28.0`, so the log shows `:compileTestJava FAILED` and then `:tckTest FAILED`.\\n\\nThere is also a mismatch between the metrics and the archived work. Metrics say the run ended in failure after 2 iterations with 0 generated LOC and ending commit `d984243351a847ba34c701d9e78c0e2f5c3acdfc`, but `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T13-11-28-225521Z.log` and generated outputs under `build/tests/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/` show a plausible fix path: move `RetryPolicy` usage to `io.opentelemetry.sdk.common.export.RetryPolicy`, add `io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-sdk-common`, replace obsolete `RetryUtil.setRetryPolicyOnDelegate(...)` coverage with `ManagedChannelUtil.toServiceConfig(...)`, and add `AuthenticatorTest` for the remaining reflective coverage. The generated outputs `build/tests/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/4aefdd897adeee976f4d7b39c673bd8d.out`, `1fc91e114822bfc84886bed0cb574317.out`, and `3731eedc10dfa3631b16a5416a271ac3.out` show `compileTestJava`, `test`, and `nativeTest` succeeding, but those changes were not preserved on the branch; the preserved branch mainly archives logs. `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log` looks successful and does not appear to be the blocker.\\n\\nPlease inspect:\\n- `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T13-09-08-376366Z.log`\\n- `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-04-28T13-11-28-225521Z.log`\\n- `logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/populate-artifact-urls/populate_artifact_urls.log`\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Recreate the candidate test changes from the archived session on top of `d984243351a847ba34c701d9e78c0e2f5c3acdfc` rather than from the preserved branch tip.\\n2. Re-run `./gradlew compileTestJava -Pcoordinates=io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`, `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`, and the native lane.\\n3. If those pass, re-run the automation or open a manual follow-up PR with the recovered test updates.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4335570936/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":24949014084,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAq4nL88AAAAFzxO-RA\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/249490