metadata/issues/comments/4366313800\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565#issuecomment-4366313800\",\"issue_url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/2565\",\"id\":4366313800,\"node_id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBECpSA\",\"user\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false},\"created_at\":\"2026-05-03T13:46:11Z\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-05-03T13:46:11Z\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated `fails-javac-compile` job failed for `io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0`.\\n\\nPreserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-2565-fails-javac-compile-io.opentelemetry-opentelemetry-exporter-common-1.28.0-e0ee8132\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage was the initial `compileTestJava` step for the generated `1.28.0` test project. In `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/gradle-test/gradle-test-2026-05-03T13-38-20-086049Z.log`, `RetryUtilTest.java` imports `io.opentelemetry.exporter.internal.retry.RetryPolicy` and calls `RetryUtil.setRetryPolicyOnDelegate(holder, RetryPolicy.getDefault())`; both symbols are missing for `1.28.0`, and Gradle reports 2 `cannot find symbol` errors.\\n\\nThe generation logs suggest the agent identified a replacement test shape, but the fix was never preserved. See `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-03T13-39-27-255525Z.log` and `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/fix-javac-fail/pi-generation-2026-05-03T13-42-42-617734Z.log`. `stats/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0/execution-metrics.json` shows `generated_loc: 0` and the same starting/ending commit (`0dbdfcbc475a67b3d4ba260725ff1d51fddae388`), so no material change landed on the preserved branch.\\n\\nThere is also a secondary runtime signal in `human-intervention-logs/io.opentelemetry:opentelemetry-exporter-common:1.28.0/native-test-verify/cycle-0-runNativeTraceImage-2026-05-03T13-43-43-512460Z.log`: `runNativeTraceImage` hits `MissingResourceRegistrationError` for `META-INF/services/javax.xml.stream.XMLOutputFactory`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Recreate and persist the `RetryUtilTest` fix for `tests/src/io.opentelemetry/opentelemetry-exporter-common/1.28.0/` so it no longer depends on removed `RetryPolicy` / `setRetryPolicyOnDelegate` APIs, then rerun the library tests.\\n2. If the compile fix passes, inspect the native trace log and add resource metadata for `META-INF/services/javax.xml.stream.XMLOutputFactory` if `runNativeTraceImage` is required for this library.\\n3. Verify the preserved branch actually contains the fix before retriggering automation, since this run finished on the same commit it started from.\",\"author_association\":\"MEMBER\",\"pin\":null,\"reactions\":{\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/comments/4366313800/reactions\",\"total_count\":0,\"+1\":0,\"-1\":0,\"laugh\":0,\"hooray\":0,\"confused\":0,\"heart\":0,\"rocket\":0,\"eyes\":0},\"performed_via_github_app\":null,\"event\":\"commented\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/subscriptions\",\"organizations_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/orgs\",\"repos_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/repos\",\"events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/events{/privacy}\",\"received_events_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/received_events\",\"type\":\"User\",\"user_view_type\":\"public\",\"site_admin\":false}},{\"id\":25107831031,\"node_id\":\"LE_lADOHlghYc8AAAABAq4nL88AAAAF2IsY9w\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/repos/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/events/25107831031\",\"actor\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\",\"id\":352820,\"node_id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjM1MjgyMA==\",\"avatar_url\":\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/352820?v=4\",\"gravatar_id\":\"\",\"url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov\",\"html_url\":\"https://github.com/vjovanov\",\"followers_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/followers\",\"following_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/following{/other_user}\",\"gists_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/gists{/gist_id}\",\"starred_url\":\"https://api.github.com/users/vjovanov/starred{/owner}{/repo}\",\"subscriptions_url\":\"h