inal/metadata-fix/codex.log`, `logs/io.netty:netty-common:4.2.1.Final/failure-analysis/codex_failure_analysis_issue_918.log`, and `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.1.115.Final/test-results-native/test/TEST-junit-jupiter.xml`.\\n\\nNext steps:\\n1. Verify whether reusing the `4.1.115.Final` Netty test project for `4.2.1.Final` is valid; if not, scaffold or adapt a dedicated `tests/src/io.netty/netty-common/4.2.1.Final` test project.\\n2. Reproduce the failing native test locally and debug the stalled `noSsl()`, `withAdaptive()`, and `withSsl()` paths, focusing on the reported deadlock/parked-thread behavior.\\n3. Reassess `metadata/io.netty/netty-common/4.2.1.Final/reachability-metadata.json` only after the test scaffold/runtime mismatch is ruled out, since the current evidence points to a native runtime hang.\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-03T11:10:56Z\",\"includesCreatedEdit\":false,\"isMinimized\":false,\"minimizedReason\":\"\",\"reactionGroups\":[],\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/918#issuecomment-4366025114\",\"viewerDidAuthor\":true}],\"createdAt\":\"2026-01-08T15:17:47Z\",\"labels\":[{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABz10A0g\",\"name\":\"library-unsupported-version\",\"description\":\"Automation found that the specific library version is not working with the current metadata.\",\"color\":\"bb366d\"},{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACPb0ftA\",\"name\":\"fails-native-image-run\",\"description\":\"Tests fail in native execution\",\"color\":\"d93f0b\"},{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACe9gtkA\",\"name\":\"human-intervention\",\"description\":\"Requires manual follow-up because automated dynamic-access coverage remained too low\",\"color\":\"B60205\"}],\"number\":918,\"title\":\"[Automation] native-image run fails for io.netty:netty-common:4.2.1.Final\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-03T11:11:03Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/918\"}\n/tmp/rhei-issue-details/4309.json:1:{\"assignees\":[],\"author\":{\"id\":\"