o new `4.2.1.Final` stats or execution metrics were generated in this worktree; only `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/{stats.json,execution-metrics.json}` exist, so dynamic-access coverage remains unavailable for the failing version.\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n- Reproduce from the preserved branch with `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final --stacktrace` and focus on the native runtime failure in `PlatformDependent0` / `AdaptivePoolingAllocator`.\\n- Compare Netty `4.1.74.Final` vs `4.2.1.Final` around STOMP encoder/decoder allocation paths to determine whether this needs additional metadata or a test/runtime adjustment outside `netty-codec-stomp` itself.\\n- Once the native failure is understood, regenerate the `4.2.1.Final` stats/metrics and confirm native tests pass before updating coverage.\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-02T15:25:11Z\",\"includesCreatedEdit\":false,\"isMinimized\":false,\"minimizedReason\":\"\",\"reactionGroups\":[],\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4309#issuecomment-4364128630\",\"viewerDidAuthor\":true},{\"id\":\"IC_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABBDdVhw\",\"author\":{\"login\":\"vjovanov\"},\"authorAssociation\":\"MEMBER\",\"body\":\"Human intervention needed\\n\\nThe automated job failed for `io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final`. Preserved work branch: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/tree/ai%2Fvjovanov%2Fhuman-intervention%2Fissue-4309-fails-native-image-run-io.netty-netty-codec-stomp-4.2.1.Final-7477b10e\\n\\nThe most likely failing stage is native-image runtime test execution, not metadata validation or native-image compilation. `logs/io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final/metadata-fix/codex.log` shows `:tckTest FAILED` with `Test for io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final failed with exit code 1`, while the generated native binary exists at `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/build/native/nativeTestCompile/io.netty.netty-codec-stomp_tests-tests`. The native JUnit report at `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/test-results-native/test/TEST-junit-jupiter.xml` shows 13 tests run, 7 passed, and 6 failed. The strongest repeated signal is `java.lang.NullPointerException` at `io.netty.util.internal.PlatformDependent0.safeConstructPutInt(...)`, reached via `ReferenceCountUpdater.setInitialValue(...)` and `AdaptivePoolingAllocator$Chunk.<init>(...)` during STOMP encoder paths. The same native report also shows decoder regressions returning empty content (`decoderAggregatesContentLengthFrameIntoFullStompFrame`, `decoderReadsNulTerminatedFrameWithoutContentLength`, `decoderPreservesEmbeddedNulBytesWhenContentLengthIsPresent`), while the JVM report at `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/build/test-results/test/TEST-io_netty.netty_codec_stomp.Netty_codec_stompTest.xml` passes 13/13, so this currently looks native-only.\\n\\nPlease inspect `logs/io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final/metadata-fix/codex.log`, `logs/io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final/failure-analysis/codex_failure_analysis_issue_4309.log`, and `tests/src/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/test-results-native/test/TEST-junit-jupiter.xml`. No `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.2.1.Final/` metrics were produced; only `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/stats.json` and `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/execution-metrics.json` exist, so dynamic-access coverage remains unavailable for `4.2.1.Final`.\\n\\nManual next steps:\\n- Reproduce from the preserved branch with `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final --stacktrace` and focus on the native runtime failure around `PlatformDependent0` / `AdaptivePoolingAllocator`.\\n- Compare Netty `4.1.74.Final` vs `4.2.1.Final` in the STOMP encoder/decoder buffer allocation path to determine whether this needs additional metadata outside `netty-codec-stomp` or a test adjustment for changed runtime behavior.\\n- After identifying the fix, rerun stats/metrics for `4.2.1.Final` and confirm native tests pass before updating coverage.\",\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-03T07:58:59Z\",\"includesCreatedEdit\":false,\"isMinimized\":false,\"minimizedReason\":\"\",\"reactionGroups\":[],\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4309#issuecomment-4365702535\",\"viewerDidAuthor\":true}],\"createdAt\":\"2026-05-02T13:33:29Z\",\"labels\":[{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABz10A0g\",\"name\":\"library-unsupported-version\",\"description\":\"Automation found that the specific library version is not working with the current metadata.\",\"color\":\"bb366d\"},{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACPb0ftA\",\"name\":\"fails-native-image-run\",\"description\":\"Tests fail in native execution\",\"color\":\"d93f0b\"},{\"id\":\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACe9gtkA\",\"name\":\"human-intervention\",\"description\":\"Requires manual follow-up because automated dynamic-access coverage remained too low\",\"color\":\"B60205\"}],\"number\":4309,\"title\":\"[Automation] native-image run fails for io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final\",\"updatedAt\":\"2026-05-03T07:59:05Z\",\"url\":\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4309\"}\n/tmp/rhei-issue-details/5185.json:1:{\"assignees\":[],\"author\":{\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjE3MjcwMzI1\",\"is_bot\":false,\"login\":\"graalvmbot\",\"name\":\"graalvm bot\"},\"body\":\"## javac compile on ubuntu-latest / JDK 25 / mode current-defaults\\n\\nFailure kind: javac compile\\nOS: ubuntu-latest\\nJDK: 25\\nNative-image mode: current-defaults\\nReproducer: `GVM_TCK_NATIVE_IMAGE_MODE=\\\"current-defaults\\\" GVM_TCK_LV=\\\"1.11.0\\\" ./gradlew clean compileTestJava -Pcoordinates=\\\"org.junit.platform:junit-platform-engine:1.10.4\\\"`\\nRunner log: https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/actions/runs/25274562434/job/74102395309\\nLast 300 lines of the log:\\n```console\\n[junit-platform-native] Running in 'test listener' mode using files matching pattern [j