tty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/stats.json` and `stats/io.netty/netty-codec-stomp/4.1.74.Final/execution-metrics.json` exist, so dynamic-access coverage remains unavailable for `4.2.1.Final`.\\\\n\\\\nManual next steps:\\\\n- Reproduce from the preserved branch with `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final --stacktrace` and focus on the native runtime failure around `PlatformDependent0` / `AdaptivePoolingAllocator`.\\\\n- Compare Netty `4.1.74.Final` vs `4.2.1.Final` in the STOMP encoder/decoder buffer allocation path to determine whether this needs additional metadata outside `netty-codec-stomp` or a test adjustment for changed runtime behavior.\\\\n- After identifying the fix, rerun stats/metrics for `4.2.1.Final` and confirm native tests pass before updating coverage.\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-05-03T07:58:59Z\\\",\\\"includesCreatedEdit\\\":false,\\\"isMinimized\\\":false,\\\"minimizedReason\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"reactionGroups\\\":[],\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://github.com/oracle/graalvm-reachability-metadata/issues/4309#issuecomment-4365702535\\\",\\\"viewerDidAuthor\\\":true}],\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-05-02T13:33:29Z\\\",\\\"labels\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAABz10A0g\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"library-unsupported-version\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Automation found that the specific library version is not working with the current metadata.\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"bb366d\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACPb0ftA\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"fails-native-image-run\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Tests fail in native execution\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"d93f0b\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"LA_kwDOHlghYc8AAAACe9gtkA\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"human-intervention\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Requires manual follow-up because automated dynamic-access coverage remained too low\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"B60205\\\"}],\\\"number\\\":4309,\\\"title\\\":\\\"[Automation] native-image run fails for io.netty:netty-codec-stomp:4.2.1.Final\\\",\\\"updatedAt\\\":\\\"2026-05-03T07